Package: streamdeb-config
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-gi, python3-pil, python3-elgato-streamdeck, gir1.2-gtk-4.0
Maintainer: Jimmy <dlocmot@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/dlocmot/streamdeb
Description: GTK4 configurator for the streamdeb Stream Deck dashboard
 streamdeb-config is the GTK4 GUI for editing the page layouts of the
 streamdeb dashboard (apps, web links, key combos, window tiling) and
 mirroring the live deck output. Talks to the streamdeb service via
 file-based IPC under /tmp/streamdeb-preview/.
